{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"569b44ccac","title":"给文润泉的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b0a093b5b6","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":7,"articleId":"569b44ccac"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"aba96eab4a","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文润泉，毛泽东的表兄。"},{"id":"babf7b3775","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"十哥，即文洋香，毛泽东的表兄。十七哥，即文枚清，毛泽东的表兄。文凯，与文润泉同宗。运昌，即文运昌，毛泽东的表兄。"},{"id":"1a52fc310a","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"南松，即文南松，毛泽东的表兄。"}],"contents":[{"id":"96592c5ea3","type":"title","text":"给文润泉的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac"},{"id":"aba96eab4a","type":"paragraph","text":"润泉表兄大鉴","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac"},{"id":"babf7b3775","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十六日来信收到，甚以为感。唐家凭现在尚有多少人，有饭吃否，十哥、十七哥还在否，便时请你告我。文凯先生宜在湖南就近解决工作问题，不宜远游，弟亦未便直接为他作介，尚乙谅之。运昌兄连来数信，已复一信寄白蚌口，不知他接到否？南松兄第二次来信已收到，感谢他的好意。此复，顺祝健康！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac"},{"id":"1a52fc310a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac"},{"id":"c3f0107828","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年五月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac"}],"page":{"id":"19cce01283","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"569b44ccac","start":337,"end":337}}}},"__N_SSG":true}